targetLookupAttribute - Variable in class netgest.bo.xwc.xeo.components.SplitedLookup
Situation: 1) The boObject returned by SplitedLookup.getTargetObject() is of XEO Model 'A'. 2) XEO Model A has an attributeObject/attributeObjectCollection (named 'P') to XEO Model B. 3) XEO Model B has an attribute 'X' of any type (usually Text/Number) The value of this property is 'X', so that one can search instances of XEO Model B by the given X attribute and assign that object to the 'P' attributeObject
